  and
  `Q_rot^A` drains `A_n`.
  Mirror and companion signs are then fixed by mandatory conjugate completion.
- `[INFERRED]` The normalized desired-channel forcing ledger is:

  ```text
  int_I |Q_clk|   = 1/6,
  int_I |Q_seed|  = mu,
  int_I |Q_amp|   = 1/3 - mu,
  int_I |Q_rot^D| = 1/4,
  int_I |Q_rot^A| = 1/12,
  int_I |Q_next|  = 1/6.
  ```

